WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.069
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.069 --> 00:00:02.966
How are you all doing today?

00:00:02.966 --> 00:00:06.600
Well, I'm Brandon Biggs and this is Diana Biggs, and this is my wife.

00:00:06.884 --> 00:00:08.591
We're excited to be with you.

00:00:08.876 --> 00:00:11.832
We have some things on our heart and we're just going to get right to it.

00:00:11.832 --> 00:00:17.571
We want to take communion with you, and we're going to pray and lift up your needs.

00:00:17.571 --> 00:00:30.750
If you have something that you have need of today, know that all things are possible to him who believes.

00:00:30.750 --> 00:00:40.760
I believe that today is your day for your healing, for your deliverance, for your miracle.

00:00:40.760 --> 00:00:43.231
Diana and I want to agree with you.

00:00:43.231 --> 00:00:45.827
We'll be your two.

00:00:46.213 --> 00:01:01.496
You may say there's nobody out there praying for me, there's nobody out there agreeing with me for anything, but you've come to the right place today.

00:01:01.496 --> 00:01:17.240
We want you to know that it wasn't by accident that you clicked this video, because there's somebody out there in your corner that's believing God with you.

00:01:17.240 --> 00:01:36.302
Ladies and gentlemen, you have two people right here who love the Lord, and we know that when we pray, we get our prayers answered because God is our friend.

00:01:36.302 --> 00:01:43.600
He visits us, and I believe with all my heart he'll visit you.

00:01:43.600 --> 00:01:57.359
He's no respecter of persons, ladies and gentlemen, and what he does for one of his kids, he'll do for all of them.

00:01:57.359 --> 00:02:00.537
It just takes faith.

00:02:00.537 --> 00:02:07.490
It just takes you reaching out in faith and believing.

00:02:07.490 --> 00:02:17.269
So we just want you to know you have somebody in your corner believing for you.

00:02:17.269 --> 00:02:26.351
Diana and I will agree with you and believe with you for your miracle today.

00:02:26.351 --> 00:02:30.074
Nothing's too big and nothing's too small.

00:02:30.074 --> 00:02:36.127
Jesus will meet you right where you are.

00:02:36.127 --> 00:02:47.333
I just want you to know that we're believing for big things, whatever you need.

00:02:53.737 --> 00:03:06.406
You could tell us, 'Brandon, I've got this and this,' and it's not going to shock us.

00:03:06.406 --> 00:03:21.223
We believe that God is able to do exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:03:26.227 --> 00:03:31.016
So we're going to take communion and believe God for the manifestation of healing and for your deliverance.

00:03:33.109 --> 00:03:45.940
You may be bound by something; you say, 'I've been dealing with this for 30 years, this alcoholism or whatever,' and you might have cirrhosis of the liver.

00:03:56.560 --> 00:04:00.844
The doctors tell you if you don't stop doing this, you're going to go home, and you think, 'How can I get free from that?

00:04:00.844 --> 00:04:06.599
' I believe today is your day.

00:04:12.920 --> 00:04:19.984
I don't know who that's for, but that just came up out of my spirit.

00:04:19.984 --> 00:04:31.663
There's somebody dealing with alcoholism; you've been bound by this and you've been hiding it.

00:04:40.016 --> 00:04:58.630
You don't want people to know that you have a problem with alcohol; you're embarrassed of this and you've been dealing with it for a long time.

00:04:58.630 --> 00:05:13.000
It's a spirit that's come to try to destroy you, but Jesus tells me today is your day.

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:26.400
You're going to get delivered from that alcoholic devil as you take communion with us.

00:05:32.740 --> 00:05:44.440
That demonic spirit that's been pestering you and driving you to drink yourself to death is going to be broken off your life today.

00:05:48.196 --> 00:05:48.511
I believe it.

00:05:48.511 --> 00:05:52.920
Today is your day of deliverance.

00:05:57.919 --> 00:06:14.759
I don't want you putting it in the comment section after you get free if you're embarrassed about it, but you can email us and tell us for privacy.

00:06:25.800 --> 00:06:26.036
You don't have to expose that, but we want to know.

00:06:26.036 --> 00:06:46.104
We want to rejoice with you that you're free, because the devil comes to kill and destroy, but the Bible says that God has come that we might have life and life more abundantly.

00:06:46.104 --> 00:07:05.249
I believe with all my heart today that the spirit of alcoholism is broken off of your life in the name of Jesus, for whom the Son has set free is free indeed.

00:07:06.217 --> 00:07:11.944
This is not just about alcoholism; it's about every kind of addiction.

00:07:11.944 --> 00:07:18.600
Fentanyl, that's a spirit too, and it grabs a hold of you.

00:07:18.600 --> 00:07:46.514
I believe from Oxycodone to fentanyl, to marijuana, to cocaine, to whatever you have need to be delivered of, I believe with all my heart from heroin to meth that you are free in the name of Jesus from these demonic spirits.

00:07:46.514 --> 00:07:50.135
I speak to them right now.

00:07:50.135 --> 00:08:06.497
Father, we lift up this body, and you said that you became sickness for us, you became addiction for us.

00:08:12.174 --> 00:08:17.128
You took all our griefs and all our pain, all of our burdens, all of our sorrows.

00:08:23.160 --> 00:08:23.480
You took it all for us.

00:08:32.413 --> 00:08:57.624
The Bible says that you were wounded for our transgressions, you were bruised for our iniquities; the chastisement of our peace was upon you and with your stripes we are healed.

00:08:58.984 --> 00:09:21.315
We take this body in the name of Jesus, and as we take this body, we have a covenant with you for deliverance, for healing, for emotional healing.

00:09:21.315 --> 00:09:30.120
I speak to emotions and trauma from being sexually abused, verbally abused, to physically abused.

00:09:30.547 --> 00:09:42.010
We speak to the trauma of that, from PTSD, and we say in the name of Jesus, be free.

00:09:42.010 --> 00:09:55.777
Let the fire of the Holy Spirit move on you and deliver you from that bondage and the baggage of that.

00:10:03.326 --> 00:10:11.360
I say in the name of Jesus Christ of Nazareth, you are free, for whom the Son has set free is free indeed.

00:10:11.360 --> 00:10:56.640
I speak to all those demonic spirits: you let her go, you let him go, and you do not bother them anymore.

00:10:56.640 --> 00:11:09.311
We call their mind healed and whole and well.

00:11:09.311 --> 00:11:55.291
Father, we take authority over those demonic spirits of torment in Jesus' name, and we say peace that passes all understanding is over your emotions today, over your mind.

00:12:22.730 --> 00:12:23.025
I hear the Holy Spirit tell me you need to get in the word and renew your mind with the water of the word.

00:12:23.025 --> 00:13:01.973
Renew your mind in the name of Jesus by the word of God, putting that word in through your eyes and your ears, listening and renewing your mind on a day-to-day basis, and that will deliver you even more.

00:13:11.569 --> 00:13:13.347
You will know the truth and the truth will keep you free.

00:13:13.347 --> 00:13:47.120
Yes, you need to know the truth of God's word and what he says about you, and that truth will set you free.

00:13:55.249 --> 00:13:58.609
You have to get that inside of you.

00:13:58.609 --> 00:14:24.760
When the devil tries to remind you of your past—'this happened to you as a child, your daddy did this, your mama did this'—you have to remind him of his future.

00:14:24.760 --> 00:14:49.280
Say, 'Satan, you reminded me of my past today; I'm going to remind you that you're going to burn in hell for eternity in the lake of fire.

00:14:49.280 --> 00:15:11.177
' There's a fire waiting for you, buddy, and every one of your devils and every one of your imps and all your spiritual wickedness in high places.

00:15:11.177 --> 00:15:23.897
There's a place for you in the fire and you're going to burn there through all eternity.

00:15:23.897 --> 00:15:30.733
I'm telling you, he'll stop doing that.

00:15:30.733 --> 00:15:43.615
If he reminds you of your past, you keep reminding him of his future.

00:15:43.615 --> 00:15:50.067
He doesn't want to hear it.

00:15:50.067 --> 00:15:58.908
Resist the devil and he will flee.

00:15:58.908 --> 00:16:09.186
Submit yourself unto God, resist the devil, and he will flee.

00:16:09.186 --> 00:16:24.374
He will scream in terror, but you've got to submit yourself.

00:16:24.374 --> 00:16:34.493
How you do that is you get in the word.

00:16:55.262 --> 00:16:55.480
I submit myself to you, I resist the devil, I will not fall into this temptation again of alcoholism.

00:16:55.480 --> 00:16:57.831
I thank you, Father.

00:17:00.831 --> 00:17:06.849
We take this body right now in Jesus' name.

00:17:06.849 --> 00:17:42.451
Lord, you're the healer, you're the deliverer, and we take authority over that spirit of alcoholism right now and we command you to get out now in the name of Jesus.

00:18:00.363 --> 00:18:01.266
Now, Lord, we plead the blood.

00:18:15.630 --> 00:18:21.540
You told us if we make much of the blood, the blood will make much of us.

00:18:47.820 --> 00:18:48.210
We make much of the blood today and we apply the blood over these circumstances, over these addictions.

00:18:49.347 --> 00:18:58.120
We apply the blood of Jesus over us and we thank you, Father, that you've set us free.

00:19:08.480 --> 00:19:08.760
We don't have to be bound by the devil's hand anymore.

00:19:09.320 --> 00:19:17.360
We take this blood and we thank you, Lord, for the blood of Jesus Christ.

00:19:22.138 --> 00:19:22.360
Thank you, Lord, for the forgiveness of our sins.

00:19:25.870 --> 00:19:33.039
For if we confess our sins, you're faithful and just to forgive us and cleanse us from all unrighteousness.

00:19:33.039 --> 00:19:34.240
Everybody say amen on that.

00:19:37.859 --> 00:19:44.720
I believe that you're free today and that devil can't stay inside; he can't torment you no more.

00:19:44.720 --> 00:19:50.898
Out of that flesh, I speak deliverance and wholeness.

00:20:03.200 --> 00:20:08.546
I speak to that demonic spirit: you break off now in Jesus' name.

00:20:08.546 --> 00:20:16.332
You go, spirit of grief, you spirit of worry, get out now.

00:20:16.332 --> 00:20:31.320
There's someone dealing with a broken marriage, a bad divorce, and then there's another person who lost a child, losing someone dear to you.

00:20:32.040 --> 00:20:47.280
It came through a spirit of depression, a spirit of heaviness, and because of that, you drank to try to cover that pain.

00:20:52.968 --> 00:20:53.244
The Lord wants to set you free.

00:20:53.244 --> 00:20:57.295
Be free today in Jesus' name.

00:20:57.295 --> 00:21:05.400
Holy Spirit, go through this camera right where they are.

00:21:05.811 --> 00:21:10.622
I believe as we pray, you receive deliverance from those addictions.

00:21:10.622 --> 00:21:23.850
I see a gambling addiction; you've been tormented by gambling so much so that it's almost destroyed you.

00:21:23.850 --> 00:21:38.297
Your finances are a wreck because of this demonic spirit that has been sent and is generational.

00:21:38.297 --> 00:21:44.000
It will end today in Jesus' name.

00:21:47.679 --> 00:21:53.647
You get your hand off of them; I break this right now and we sever this.

00:21:53.647 --> 00:21:59.924
It's online gambling; credit card debt has mounted up.

00:22:03.039 --> 00:22:08.600
Father, I praise you and thank you that you're setting these people free today.

00:22:08.600 --> 00:22:17.149
They'll turn their life around by the word of God.

00:22:17.149 --> 00:22:27.466
Lord, we believe we receive your deliverance, healing, and all that you have for us.

00:22:28.693 --> 00:22:37.945
We speak life over the bodies and we speak healing, wholeness, and wellness over them.

00:22:47.159 --> 00:22:47.519
We command the demonic spirit of depression and anxiety to go now.

00:22:47.519 --> 00:22:55.520
Bipolar disorder, we speak to you to go now.

00:22:55.520 --> 00:23:02.209
Healing and wholeness is over their minds.

00:23:02.209 --> 00:23:13.000
Father, I thank you their hormones are lined up; serotonin levels are lining up, dopamine levels are lining up.

00:23:13.000 --> 00:23:22.308
We thank you, Father, that you have taken it all on the cross for us.

00:23:22.308 --> 00:23:26.670
We won't take Satan's package anymore.

00:23:26.670 --> 00:23:34.040
Father, I thank you for healing over their bodies today.

00:23:34.040 --> 00:23:36.244
Fibromyalgia is being healed right now.

00:23:43.346 --> 00:23:43.537
We speak to fibromyalgia and call you whole and well in Jesus' name.

00:23:43.537 --> 00:23:48.840
Lyme disease—I just saw Lyme disease from ticks.

00:23:48.840 --> 00:23:51.573
The Lord showed me a tick.

00:23:51.573 --> 00:24:01.740
I say in the name of Jesus, you are free from Lyme disease from a tick bite.

00:24:01.740 --> 00:24:06.391
Thank you, Father, for that anointing going through this camera right now.

00:24:19.439 --> 00:24:19.639
We speak to that Lyme disease and call that blood pure in Jesus' name.

00:24:19.639 --> 00:24:22.694
Every cell, every fiber of that body be healed.

00:24:33.996 --> 00:24:34.333
Father, I saw chronic migraine headaches.

00:24:37.728 --> 00:24:42.960
I say in the name of Jesus, you are free from these headaches, these demonic strongholds.

00:24:42.960 --> 00:24:48.346
It's actually a demonic spirit trying to attach itself.

00:24:58.502 --> 00:24:58.751
We call you out, headache devil, go now.

00:24:58.751 --> 00:25:01.421
Grinding of the teeth—it's habitual worrying.

00:25:01.421 --> 00:25:05.164
Cast all your cares upon him, for he cares for you.

00:25:05.164 --> 00:25:07.491
Take no thought for tomorrow.

00:25:07.491 --> 00:25:16.188
Let the peace that passes all understanding flow over your mind today.

00:25:16.188 --> 00:25:20.457
Completely delivered from those headaches, completely delivered from TMJ.

00:25:20.457 --> 00:25:32.050
Father, I lift these women up who are believing God to conceive a child and I call their wombs to be healed in Jesus' name.

00:25:32.050 --> 00:25:36.702
Body, conceive in the name of Jesus.

00:25:40.342 --> 00:25:43.706
We speak to the Fallopian tubes, the ovaries, everything functioning as it should.

00:25:43.706 --> 00:25:54.600
Father, I thank you that you bless their fruit and rebuke the devourer for our sake.

00:26:08.190 --> 00:26:08.520
I thank you that they have healthy pregnancies, long and full-term.

00:26:08.520 --> 00:26:14.990
You said our vine will not cast its fruit before its time.

00:26:14.990 --> 00:26:27.674
So Father, I thank you that there is life in their wombs, that they would have easy pregnancies and no postpartum depression.

00:26:31.560 --> 00:26:32.760
I rebuke postpartum depression in the name of Jesus.

00:26:43.124 --> 00:26:44.209
You shall not rob these women of the joy of being a new mother.

00:26:44.209 --> 00:26:52.320
There is no weapon formed against them or these babies that shall prosper.

00:26:53.440 --> 00:27:10.129
For the whole person—their spirit, soul, and body—no Down syndrome, no autism in the name of Jesus, no cerebral palsy or birth defects.

00:27:12.110 --> 00:27:18.039
I just saw birth defects; we pray for the arms, fingers, toes.

00:27:18.039 --> 00:27:21.919
You will have everything, missing nothing, broken nothing.

00:27:21.919 --> 00:27:28.240
Creative miracles over the limbs and the amniotic fluid.

00:27:28.240 --> 00:27:30.186
Thank you, Lord.

00:27:35.960 --> 00:27:36.305
We call forth healing and wholeness in there.

00:27:36.305 --> 00:27:45.327
We thank you, Lord, that these mothers will not have to go on bed rest.

00:27:45.327 --> 00:27:49.314
No cleft palates—I saw that in the spirit too.

00:27:49.314 --> 00:27:53.655
Father, we speak healing over cleft palates in Jesus' name.

00:27:53.655 --> 00:28:00.124
Heart defects—we speak to heart defects and holes in the heart.

00:28:09.226 --> 00:28:09.492
We call heart defects healed.

00:28:13.519 --> 00:28:30.280
We call the baby's heart to be formed and completely whole, and that they would be flipped down as they're supposed to, not breech.

00:28:30.280 --> 00:28:37.400
No cords wrapped around the neck in Jesus' name.

00:28:44.769 --> 00:28:45.098
And their Apgar scores—they wouldn't have to be on oxygen.

00:28:45.426 --> 00:28:48.175
We call you to be healthy.

00:28:48.175 --> 00:28:51.840
Mothers, you speak to your child.

00:28:51.840 --> 00:28:57.629
You have authority over your baby.

00:28:57.629 --> 00:29:08.485
Lay your hands on your stomach and pray blessing over your baby.

00:29:08.485 --> 00:29:15.156
Flip and be right; come out whenever it's time, no breech.

00:29:15.156 --> 00:29:32.070
If they say we're going to have to induce you because it's been too long, I call you to come out of there in Jesus' name.

00:29:32.070 --> 00:29:35.129
That's what we did.

00:29:35.129 --> 00:29:51.935
We took communion, laid hands on Diana's stomach, and told each one it's time for you to come forth now.

00:30:04.519 --> 00:30:04.809
You're full-term, you come out; we're not going to be induced.

00:30:15.300 --> 00:30:15.570
We have authority over you as mommy and daddy.

00:30:25.133 --> 00:30:25.364
We tell you to come out now in Jesus' name.

00:30:25.364 --> 00:30:38.248
Now, look at the date and see if it's full-term; don't do it prematurely, but the Lord gives us instinct.

00:30:38.248 --> 00:30:50.120
If that doctor tells you, 'We're going to have to induce,' say no, we're going to speak to this baby to come forth.

00:30:50.120 --> 00:30:53.387
I take communion and have authority.

00:30:53.387 --> 00:30:57.360
I call you healthy, I call you blessed, little baby.

00:30:57.360 --> 00:31:03.119
I speak to your mind and eyes to develop like they're supposed to.

00:31:03.119 --> 00:31:05.309
Nothing missing, nothing broken.

00:31:05.309 --> 00:31:17.666
Then we would take a seed and sow a seed for the harvest.

00:31:17.666 --> 00:31:30.420
We'd say, 'Father, we thank you, we plant this into good ground, and we thank you there's a covering over this with a financial seed.

00:31:30.420 --> 00:31:34.909
' I saw that in the spirit when I was praying.

00:31:34.909 --> 00:31:39.770
We can educate a little bit here about what we do.

00:31:39.770 --> 00:31:40.929
It's needed.

00:31:40.929 --> 00:31:49.208
Anointing your stomach with oil and believing God.

00:31:49.208 --> 00:32:00.399
We would take a seed and sow it to a ministry and say, 'Lord, we thank you that there's blessing on it.

00:32:00.399 --> 00:32:07.399
' David said he would not give God an offering that didn't cost him something.

00:32:07.399 --> 00:32:13.480
That's what made it valuable, because it was worship from the heart.

00:32:13.480 --> 00:32:19.669
When it came to my children, I wanted to sow for their peace.

00:32:19.669 --> 00:32:28.126
I give, and it shall be given unto me, good measure, pressed down, shaken together.

00:32:28.126 --> 00:32:34.868
I sowed an offering of thanks for a healthy baby.

00:32:34.868 --> 00:32:41.873
I'm not manipulating God; we gave it as an offering of worship.

00:32:41.873 --> 00:32:57.320
I didn't want to give something that didn't cost me something, but to say, 'God, thank you for a healthy child.

00:32:57.320 --> 00:33:05.405
' It may be a hundred bucks, fifty bucks, twenty bucks, or a dollar.

00:33:05.720 --> 00:33:08.772
You may be living on a dollar.

00:33:08.772 --> 00:33:12.364
'Father, I give this dime to you.

00:33:12.364 --> 00:33:22.049
' There's been times when we sowed a pencil, whatever we found on the floor.

00:33:22.049 --> 00:33:40.231
At the beginning of the year, I sow a significant seed to the Lord for the year to be blessed.

00:33:40.231 --> 00:33:45.459
In 2025, we'll do it again.

00:33:45.459 --> 00:33:53.247
'Father, we sow this as an offering of thanksgiving to you.

00:33:53.247 --> 00:33:58.719
We sow into 2025 believing for a financial blessing.

00:33:58.719 --> 00:34:03.949
' We always give a sacrificial seed.

00:34:03.949 --> 00:34:09.754
God says, 'I'm going to give this by faith.

00:34:09.754 --> 00:34:22.091
' Write down what you're believing for in 2025 and take communion over it.

00:34:22.091 --> 00:34:24.629
Believe God for big.

00:34:24.629 --> 00:34:37.599
Closing out 2024, don't let go of it yet—we still have 50-some days left—but believe God going into 2025.

00:34:42.919 --> 00:34:47.434
We sow a seed believing for a harvest over our finances.

00:34:47.434 --> 00:35:03.787
Father, we thank you that 2025 will be an amazing year, exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

00:35:10.700 --> 00:35:10.840
That's how we lived our life.

00:35:22.726 --> 00:35:23.131
We give offerings of thanks ahead of time.

00:35:28.220 --> 00:35:30.755
That's action in faith—giving him thank yous before you even receive it in the natural.

00:35:30.755 --> 00:35:32.992
Without faith, it's impossible to please God.

00:35:32.992 --> 00:35:42.029
You sow into good ground, your church, wherever the Lord tells you, and you give that offering of thanks.

00:35:45.204 --> 00:35:48.959
Every single time, we write down our vision and what we're believing for and we take communion over it.

00:35:48.959 --> 00:35:55.103
We fold it up and put it in a place where we don't see it again until the end of the year.

00:35:55.103 --> 00:35:59.260
It's amazing to see what God did.

00:35:59.260 --> 00:36:09.685
When you take communion and put God first by giving offerings of thanksgiving starting out the year—do it on New Year's Day.

00:36:09.685 --> 00:36:16.980
I don't do it ahead of time because I'm still believing for 2024.

00:36:16.980 --> 00:36:25.920
But I'm feeling in my heart to tell you this so you can start meditating on it.

00:36:31.809 --> 00:36:32.040
Write down what you're believing for.

00:36:32.040 --> 00:36:40.900
It could be a new car, a new house, or a new husband if you're single.

00:36:53.140 --> 00:36:53.345
You don't want to be alone anymore.

00:36:53.345 --> 00:36:54.500
Write it down.

00:36:54.500 --> 00:36:59.228
'God, I'm believing for a spouse this year.

00:36:59.228 --> 00:37:12.939
' I'd take that a step further: write down specific qualities that you desire in a mate.

00:37:12.939 --> 00:37:18.640
You don't want to be unequally yoked with unbelievers.

00:37:18.640 --> 00:37:34.629
Don't think you're getting some Bubba who has all these problems and you think, 'Well, God sent me this Ishmael.

00:37:34.629 --> 00:37:42.196
' It's an Ishmael, and Isaac is around the corner.

00:37:42.196 --> 00:37:53.380
Don't settle for an Ishmael because you think Bubba came and he's not what you were believing for.

00:37:53.380 --> 00:37:58.220
He's not saved; he doesn't love the Lord.

00:38:08.546 --> 00:38:08.737
The Lord might have brought him and he's a Bubba, and you go, 'Who?

00:38:08.737 --> 00:38:20.920
